商业思维\t❹ 线上p图大师美图秀秀就能搞定，我都会p[害羞R]回购.率很高，无成ben经营，快去试试还有会ppt的，写文案的，起名字的等等技能get\t❺ 小红书卖苹果想象不到利润这么高吧[暗中观察R]不仅能卖苹果，只要会搞流量，都是\t▫️最后敏哥想说行动力才是决定你和别人拉开差距的关键我前面一直跟大家说，普通人机会在自媒体投入成ben小，几乎为0，但天花.板高而且适用于各行各业嫁接资源普通人在这个阶段保持在不断学新技能，累积经验就已经超越很多一动不动的对手了我是敏哥，八年互联网连续创业者希望在这里能结交一群志同道合的创业朋友 #创业# #副业#","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/content","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 426, 108)","boundsInScreen":"(588, 2712 - 1014, 2260)"},{"index":1,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 106)","boundsInScreen":"(555, 2820 - 1047, 2260)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"敏哥说钱","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mPublishNameView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 132, 45)","boundsInScreen":"(649, 2850 - 781, 2260)"},{"index":1,"resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudLayout","class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 143, 50)","boundsInScreen":"(904, 2848 - 1047, 2260)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"231","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudCountView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"check